title: 163: Arctic Breeze
description: Sal, Adam and Justin are giddy. What's in the air? The cannabis club next has moved out of the building so it's not that. In this episode they talk about the first Mind Pump live event and provide a fitness tip for good measure. Post on Instagram through Oct 17, 2015 to win a free T-Shirt and be interviewed on Mind Pump! Listen to the episode for more details. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
